layout.house_prompt: A co-working space with an open office, two meeting rooms, a lounge, a kitchen, a reception, and a bathroom. The open office has four desks with chairs and computers. The first meeting room has a conference table with six chairs. The second meeting room has a whiteboard and four chairs. The lounge has two sofas and a coffee table. The kitchen has a refrigerator and a microwave on a counter. The reception has a reception desk with a computer. The bathroom has a toilet and a sink.

reception.text_description: A modern minimalist co-working space reception area with a reception desk and a computer.

open_office.text_description: A modern minimalist open office co-working area with four desks, each with a chair and a computer.

hallway.text_description: A modern minimalist quiet corridor/vestibule providing acoustic separation between the open office and enclosed rooms.

meeting_room.text_description: A modern minimalist meeting room with a conference table and six chairs.

bathroom.text_description: A modern minimalist bathroom with a toilet and a sink.

lounge.text_description: A modern minimalist lounge area with two sofas and a coffee table.

kitchen.text_description: A modern minimalist kitchenette with a refrigerator and a microwave on a counter.
